  (str ministry) (str `Ministry of Social Justice and Empowerment`)
  (str department) (str `Department of Social Justice and Empowerment`)
  (str longTitle) (str `An Act to provide for the prohibition of employment of manual scavengers as well as construction or continuance of dry latrines and for the regulation of construction and maintenance of water-seal latrines and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`)
